The '''1994 Estoril Open''' was a [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Tennis court#Clay courts|outdoor clay courts]]. This event was the 5th edition of the [[Portugal Open|Estoril Open]], included in the [[1994 ATP Tour]] [[ATP International Series|World Series]]. The event took place at the [[Estoril Court Central]], in [[Oeiras Municipality, Portugal|Oeiras]], [[Portugal]], from March 28 through April 4, 1994.

==Winners==
===Men's Singles===
{{main|1994 Estoril Open – Men's Singles}}
{{flagicon|ESP}} '''[[Carlos Costa (tennis)|Carlos Costa]]''' def. {{flagicon|UKR}} [[Andrei Medvedev]], 4&ndash;6, 7&ndash;5, 6&ndash;4
*It was Costa's 1st title of the year and 5th of his career. It was his 2nd title at Estoril.

===Men's Doubles===
{{main|1994 Estoril Open – Men's Doubles}}
{{flagicon|ITA}} '''[[Cristian Brandi]]''' / {{flagicon|ITA}} '''[[Federico Mordegan]]''' def. {{flagicon|NED}} [[Richard Krajicek]] / {{flagicon|NED}} [[Menno Oosting]], W/O

