{{Infobox football club | clubname = ASF| image = | fullname = ASF Fianarantsoa| nickname = | founded = | ground = ?, [[Madagascar]]| capacity = | chairman = | manager = | league = [[THB Champions League]] | season = | position = | }}
'''ASF Fianarantsoa''' is a Malagasy football club based in [[Madagascar]] who currently plays in the [[Malagasy Second Division]].
In 1990 the club has won the [[THB Champions League]].<ref>http://www.foot-base.com/en/CAF/Madagascar/ASF_Fianarantsoa/</ref>
