'''Deportivo Azogues''' is an Ecuadorian [[Association football|football]] club based in [[Azogues]]. It plays in the [[Ecuadorian Serie B|Serie B]], the second tier of professional football in Ecuador. It plays its home games at the [[Estadio Municipal Jorge Andrade Cantos]].
