'''Kpando Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Kpandu]],in the Volta Region of [[Ghana]].  It used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Heart of Lions]] of the [[Ghana Premier League]].  The stadium holds 5,000 spectators.

